      <title>阿狐の小纸条</title>
      <link href="/2022/05/17/%E9%98%BF%E7%8B%90%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%B8%E6%9D%A1/"/>
      <url>/2022/05/17/%E9%98%BF%E7%8B%90%E7%9A%84%E7%BA%B8%E6%9D%A1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>#March 9<br><strong>The distance between us is breaking my spirit.</strong></p><p><strong>My time and experiences without you are meaningless to me.🌹</strong></p><p><strong>谢谢你，让我知道原来世界上，真的有人那么可爱！晚上要好好学习，我喜欢你为梦想努力的样子！如果我是那只路过的玫瑰也没关系，只希望，送给你花香，不会刺伤你。</strong>🌟</p><p>#March 10<br><strong>U had me at “hello”<br>Your destiny was entwined with mine!</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
